etsysNetflowMIB.name: etsysNetflowMIB

revisions.description: Clarify that the translation provided by this MIB is only applicable to NetFlow Version 5 export frames.
The initial version of this MIB module.

etsysNetflowMIB.contactinfo: Postal: Enterasys Networks 50 Minuteman Rd. Andover, MA 01810-1008 USA Phone: +1 978 684 1000 E-mail: support@enterasys.com WWW: http://www.enterasys.com
etsysNetflowMIB.description: This MIB module defines a portion of the SNMP MIB under the Enterasys Networks enterprise OID pertaining to configuration of Netflow on a device.

etsysNetflowExportIntfMapTable.name: etsysNetflowExportIntfMapTable
etsysNetflowExportIntfMapTable.description: A table of mappings from the Netflow version 5 export record interfaces to MIB-II ifIndex.

etsysNetflowExportIntfMapEntry.name: etsysNetflowExportIntfMapEntry
etsysNetflowExportIntfMapEntry.description: An entry containing per interface mapping of Netflow version 5 export record interfaces to MIB-II ifIndex.

etsysNetflowExportIntf.name: etsysNetflowExportIntf
etsysNetflowExportIntf.description: The interface number used in the 16 bit interface fields of Netflow version 5 export records.

etsysNetflowIfIndex.name: etsysNetflowIfIndex
etsysNetflowIfIndex.description: The MIB-II ifIndex of the interface bound to etsysNetflowExportIntf.

etsysNetflowIfIndexMapTable.name: etsysNetflowIfIndexMapTable
etsysNetflowIfIndexMapTable.description: A table of mappings from MIB-II ifIndex to Netflow export record interfaces.

etsysNetflowIfIndexMapEntry.name: etsysNetflowIfIndexMapEntry
etsysNetflowIfIndexMapEntry.description: An entry containing per interface mapping of MIB-II ifIndex to Netflow version 5 export record interfaces.

etsysNetflowExportInterface.name: etsysNetflowExportInterface
etsysNetflowExportInterface.description: The 16 bit interface number used in the interface fields of Netflow version 5 export records that is bound to the specified ifIndex.

etsysNetflowIntfMapGroup.name: etsysNetflowIntfMapGroup
etsysNetflowIntfMapGroup.description: The interface mapping group for all devices supporting Netflow version 5 export records.

etsysNetflowIntfMapCompliance.name: etsysNetflowIntfMapCompliance
etsysNetflowIntfMapCompliance.description: The compliance statement for devices that support Netflow.
